author: alally
msg: Fix Eclipse plugin build.  Eclipse JARs are now obtained from a public repository at maven.org.
Resource files are in the correct locations under src/main/resources and are added to plugin assemblies.
Fixed some errors in plugin manifest files.
Fixed some incorrect resource names due to package renamings.
